## About this folder

This folder is a **reference for every kind of media** you can embed in an MMX page: regular images, inline icons, audio, video, and iframes.

Pick one of the pages below to see how each media type is written in MMX:

- **Audios** — the `!!(path/to/audio)` block directive.
- **Videos** — the `!!!(path/to/video)` block directive.
- **Images** — the `![](path/to/image)` block directive (with optional caption / alignment classes).
- **Inline images** — the `<-path->` inline syntax, useful for tiny icons inside running text.
- **Iframes** — the `#iframe(...)` directive for embedding other pages.
